Note:
Runa Scientific Computing: Linear Algebra Decomposition (Compatibility Layer)

This is a compatibility wrapper that imports from the unified math linear algebra engine.
All functionality has been moved to math/engine/linalg for better architecture.
:End Note

Import "math/engine/linalg/decomposition" as DecompEngine

Note: Re-export all decomposition functions
Process called "lu_factorization" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return DecompEngine.lu_factorization with matrix as matrix

Process called "qr_factorization" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return DecompEngine.qr_factorization with matrix as matrix

Process called "cholesky_factorization" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return DecompEngine.cholesky_factorization with matrix as matrix

Process called "singular_value_decomposition" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return DecompEngine.singular_value_decomposition with matrix as matrix

Process called "eigen_decomposition" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return DecompEngine.eigen_decomposition with matrix as matrix

Process called "schur_decomposition" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return DecompEngine.schur_decomposition with matrix as matrix

Process called "hessenberg_decomposition" that takes matrix as Any returns Any:
    Return DecompEngine.hessenberg_decomposition with matrix as matrix